ygData.messageBody:
I was there on a guild raid a good while back so I must have been about level
20 or 22.  I was in LOIO and ran through FM with my guild.  I don't know
about going there alone and finding groups.  But I do know there was some
good exp and loot with those giants...  If you go, good luck.  

Lena
